# Build artifacts that must never enter the image build context.
# They contain host-specific (Windows) paths that break Linux container restores
# and bloat the context.

# .NET
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/TestResults/

# Node / frontend
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
.pnpm-store/
.nx/
.angular/
.vite/

# VCS / IDE / infra state
.git/
.github/
**/.terraform/
**/terraform.tfstate*
**/*.user
**/*.suo

# Local env / secrets
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/*.env.example
